@name           Mozilla Developer Network - Dark Theme
@namespace      USO Archive
@author         Vinyl Darkscratch-Kazotetsu
@description    `A dark theme for the MDN web docs pages (developer.mozilla.org), updated for compatibility with their new Yari layout engine.  Colors are adjustable via the variables set on :root.Any issues?  Additional websites to add?  Want to check out my other dark theme styles?  Let me know by contacting me through my social media (and please provide a screenshot if possible): https://www.queengoob.org/darkthemes`
